arm_group.description:
Four treatments of 150 mg Dabigatran etexilate (single oral administration) in a fixed sequence.
Single oral administration of dabigatran etexilate on Day 1;
Oral administration of 600 mg rifampicin q.d. in the evening for 7 days (Days 2 to 8) followed by an oral morning dose of dabigatran etexilate on Day 9;
Single oral administration of dabigatran etexilate on Day 16, after 7 days of rifampicin washout;
Single oral administration of dabigatran etexilate on Day 23, after 14 days of rifampicin washout
